ification" title=3D"Statistical classification">classifier</a> combines thi=
s model with a <a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Decision_rule" titl=
e=3D"Decision rule">decision rule</a>. One common rule is to pick the hypot=
hesis that is most probable so as to minimize the probability of misclassif=
ication; this is known as the <i><a href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/M=
aximum_a_posteriori" class=3D"mw-redirect" title=3D"Maximum a posteriori">m=
aximum <i>a posteriori</i></a></i> or <i>MAP</i> decision rule. The corresp=
