<div class=3D"mw-heading mw-heading4"><h4 id=3D"Testing">Testing</h4><span =
class=3D"mw-editsection"><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a =
href=3D"https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=3DNaive_Bayes_classifier=
&amp;action=3Dedit&amp;section=3D14" title=3D"Edit section: Testing"><span>=
edit</span></a><span class=3D"mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></div>
<p>Below is a sample to be classified as male or female.
</p>
